## Any other business

As it was the AGM and the annual election had been completed the
officer election was held. All existing post holders were prepared to
stand for re-election and no one else expressed an interest in standing
at this time.

Vote on extending the current officer
(bdale,Ganneff,Noodles,schultmc) terms for an additional year

